The '''[[Palpatine Mine Network]]''' was the term for the vast array of [[Space mine/Legends|space mines]] set up under the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] by [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]. Following the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], jack-of-all-trades [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] assisted in the dismantling of the Network.

After an accident of unknown origin, [[Baobab family|Baobab]] was one of only two survivors found aboard the minesweeping craft ''[[Rodrigo Andrera]]''.

